metadata.name: Skull Ape Gang Hidden #1
metadata.description: Skull Ape Gang is a Collection of 8888 NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain with no more to be minted. Each Ape is a unique 1 of 1 generated Ape from 495 Traits. We created this project for all the ape and skull lovers around the world who want to belong to the SAG Community. Our apes are not just cool JPEG, they give you proof of ownership and some of them are also very rare !
